snippet.title: Stella Sora Teaser PV「Return of the Tyrant」
snippet.description:
A thousand years have passed, and the true history has crumbled away like weathered parchment.
Yet, the world still trembles at the mention of the name "Tyrant."

Your legacy awaits, Tyrant.
